Ubuntu Tweak 0.4.5
=================

New features:

* Cleaner now can clean the package configs.
* Added a preferences dialog for Ubuntu Tweak.
* Default launch feature for Ubuntu Tweak.
* Friendly debug information.

Bug fixes:
* DropBox repository is out-of-date. (LP: #308395)
* Update Manager doesn't work. (LP: #308400)
* Repository is not signed. (LP: #312175)
* Add/Remove incorrect dialog (LP: #316191)
* Incorrect templates of ODS files. (LP: #308479)
* Typo. (LP: #310165, LP: #322057)
* Templates can't open. (LP: #319380)

Other changes:
* Rewrite the convert scripts.
* Process the status of app install/remove
* Rewrite the factory, now more powerful and flexible.
* Make the GNOME Panel icon setting revertable
* Signed every PPA repos.
